---------------------------------------------------------Open Account -----------------------------------------------------

1. new Account opening (Application number should be auto generate )
	(page 1: personal details) 
		{name ,mobile number(unique), father name , dob, Gender , email,marital status, Address ,city , pin code , state }
	(page 2: additional details)
		{religion, category , income, educational details , occupation, pan number , Aadhaar number ,  senior  citizen  , existing account (true or false)}
	(page 3: account details)
		account type : {saving account , fixed deposit account , current Account , recurring deposit account}
		Account number(16 digit number)(auto generate by system default pin)(should unique)
		pin(4 digit numeric)(auto generate by system default pin)
		cvv number (3 digit numeric)(auto generate by system)
		card number(16 digit numeric for ATM card)(auto generate by system)
		transactions id : should be auto generate and unique(combination of numbers and alphabets)
		service requirement (check boxes){ATM card, internet banking , mobile banking , email alter, cheque book, e-statements}
		
	(page 4: Deposit opening fees)
		Enter opening fees amount.
		

	check box: (I hereby declares that above entered corrects to best to the my knowledge)


	-> after submit the all details account number ,card number and pin should be generate automatic by the system.

2. check balance(means balance enquiry).
3. Deposit(if I am entering any amount means it should be add in the existing balance).
4. Cash withdrawal(transaction in other accounts meaning if I am entering any amount means it should be minus given account to total balance and individual balance as well).

5. all transactions of Account holder(means deposit , withdrawal  ).
5. mini statements of Account holder{meaning }(between given days like 15 days, 30 days , 6 months , all statements).
6.pin change

