------------------------------------------------------FD (Fixed Deposit) --------------------------------------------------------------------
FD is some amount for some Tenure(limited time) and interest wil be calculate 8%/ year and will add calculated amount in the FD account.
amount should be deduct to total balance.
1. Apply for FD
{ Name , Age , FD Account ,  Tenure , Account number  }






	


	